                    <li><span class="highlight">Sustainability Focus:</span> 50% reduction in CO2 emissions by reducing commute times</li>
                    <li><span class="highlight">Direction-Based Booking:</span> Unique visual interface showing available spaces by compass direction</li>
                    <li><span class="highlight">Profit Sharing:</span> Space owners keep 70% of revenue, creating win-win partnerships</li>
